Description:
 The new version of a popular operating system received the name Windows 10 from the Microsoft company though the previous large release went under the name Windows 8. Transition to Windows 10 reflects at once desire of the company to separate from not really popular previous version. For this reason as it is reported, the ninth version was passed: transition from the eighth to the tenth is urged to symbolize at once a huge step forward, to orientation to the Internet and to mobile users. In Microsoft called Windows 10 "the most powerful platform in the history". The vice-president of Microsoft for operating systems Terry Meyerson conducting presentations reported that Windows 10 will be established on wider range of devices of various type in comparison with the previous versions. In number of these devices, according to the presented presentation, enter not only desktop personal computers, laptops and tablets, but also smartphones, and TVs now
